      <title>日本新首相将由自民党领袖选举决定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/japan-s-new-prime-minister-to-be-decided-by-ldp-leadership-poll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本执政党将于周五选出新一任国家领导人，其成员将决定是否继续逐渐摆脱对央行支持的过度依赖、加快缓慢的改革进程或扭转过度刺激的局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/japan-s-new-prime-minister-to-be-decided-by-ldp-leadership-poll</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 23:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
